===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*med-}}
1530s, from {{der|en|la|accommodatus|accommodātus}}, perfect passive participle of {{m|la|accommodo|accommodō}}; {{m|la|ad}} + {{m|la|commodō||make fit, help}}; {{m|la|com-}} + {{m|la|modus||measure, proportion}} (English {{m|en|mode}}).

